input-
a problem 

Process
prompt the user enter his/her question 
evaluate the question 
end the process if the user enters "Q" or "I am feeling great"
split the sentence the user inputed 
store the splitted sentence in an array 
replace the i to u, me to u, my to ur, am to are 
output the question if the user enters sth else 


Output- 
the problem back to the user 

